<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .otp-code { 
            font-size: 24px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 2px dashed #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 20px; 
            font-size: 12px; 
            color: #777; 
            text-align: center;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #FF9800;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
            <p>Your OTP code for account verification is:</p>
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otpCode %></div>
            <p class="warning">This code will expire in 5 minutes. Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>
            <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Sattech. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>